%spark

var meanFahrTable = sqlContext.sql("select * from mean_fahrenheit_temp")
var meanFahrByKeyTable = sqlContext.sql("select * from mean_fahrenheit_by_key_temp")
var timestamp = sqlContext.sql("select timestamp from mqtt_message_temp order by timestamp DESC limit 1")

timestamp = timestamp.withColumn("id", (col("timestamp")-col("timestamp")) )
meanFahrTable = meanFahrTable.withColumn("id", (col("mean_fahrenheit") - col("mean_fahrenheit")))
meanFahrByKeyTable = meanFahrByKeyTable.withColumn("id", (col("mean_fahrenheit_by_key") - col("mean_fahrenheit_by_key")))

var df = meanFahrTable.as("df1")
    .join(meanFahrByKeyTable.as("df2"), meanFahrTable("id") === meanFahrByKeyTable("id"), "inner")
    .select("df1.id","df1.mean_fahrenheit", "df2.mean_fahrenheit_by_key")

df = df.as("df1")
    .join(timestamp.as("df2"), df("id") === timestamp("id"), "inner")
    .select("df2.timestamp","df1.mean_fahrenheit", "df1.mean_fahrenheit_by_key")

Try(sqlContext.sql("CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS kafka_means_fahrenheit (timestamp string, mean_fahrenheit string, mean_fahrenheit_by_key string)"))
Try(sqlContext.dropTempTable("mean_fahrenheit_temp"))
df.registerTempTable("mean_fahrenheit_temp")
Try(sqlContext.sql("INSERT INTO TABLE kafka_means_fahrenheit SELECT * FROM mean_fahrenheit_temp"))

%spark

import org.apache.spark.mllib.clustering.{KMeans, KMeansModel}
import org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.Vectors

var test = sqlContext.sql("select humedad, fahrenheit, timestamp, fecha, id from gen_test_data")
//var test = sqlContext.sql("select humedad, fahrenheit, timestamp, fecha, row_number() over () as id from mqtt_message_temp")
test  = test.withColumn("humedad", test("humedad").cast(DoubleType))
test = test.withColumn("fahrenheit", test("fahrenheit").cast(DoubleType))

val parsedTest = test.map(r => Vectors.dense(r.getDouble(0).toDouble, r.getDouble(1).toDouble)).cache()


val sameModel = KMeansModel.load(sc, "/user/zeppelin/kmeansModel")

var cnt = 0 
val result = sameModel.predict(parsedTest).collect().map(i => {cnt+=1;  (cnt,i)} ) //.map(x=> (row_number(), x))
var resultDf = sc.parallelize(result).toDF("id","cluster")

test.show()
resultDf.show()

var resultPointsDf = resultDf.as("df1")
    .join(test.as("df2"), resultDf("id") === test("id"), "inner")
    .select("df2.timestamp", "df2.fecha", "df2.humedad","df2.fahrenheit", "df1.cluster")
    
z.show(resultPointsDf)
